<br>
I am trying to gather ideas about class balancing because i got a hold of the VI's presidents e-mail. I wanted to know your ideas for class balancing, what should be improved and such. I would also like to know if i should send the letter to the president or not, or if you know any other e-mails i should send it to. Here are my thoughts on class balancing:<br>
<br>
More/better buffs<br>
More/better spells from 1-50<br>
More mana efficient/Quick spell casting time spells.<br>
Bigger mana pool<br>
and this is just my cool and wacky idea, but perhaps 2 or 3 1hs's for wizards only, that you have to quest for, and you can start to get them at lvl 15, then get the next one at 30+, and the last at 50+, with stats like 11/29, 9/26, something with a 2 or 3 ratio, some stats and possibly an effect.<br>
<br>
My 2cp, Send replies with your ideas, and other peeps i should send it too, should i bother sending a letter to the president and also your reasons. thanks.<br>
<br>
Yizzien Darkbringer<br>
Dark Elf wizard soon to be on Sullon Zek.<br>
